column5:
Aloha,

I am looking to contact the hiring team/manager for Maui Wellness, LLC. 
Is this the Maui Wellness that received the Medical Marijuana license? It is a bit confusing as there are multiple Maui Wellness companies on Maui. I found this website by linking to it from Teri Freitas Gorman's Linked In account, as she is listed as the spokesperson in an article I read.
So, my apologies if this is wrong business, but if I am contacting the correct Maui Wellness, I would like to submit a resume for a Master Grower position. 
Please contact me via email.
Looking forward to hearing from you.

Thanks!
Dean Madore
